政權。 CIA探員桑德斯（約翰尼德普 Johnny Depp 飾）得知了巴羅瑞的陰謀，於是，他找到了埃爾。曾經的鐵血戰士埃爾當然不會袖手旁觀，他終於重出江湖。但是，事情並沒有表面的那麼簡單，墨西哥荒漠上一出傳奇正在徐徐上演..<br />\n<br />\n6 10PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"474402996a2e15dffaa56ab9aa8c652ba9dc3fbb","tid":151960,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T10:40:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45f0f62297cbdfdc07146f18458ed6ec3683dd8c","tid":151960,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T11:49:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee4ab153296d6e9783f7b47b3c0d192742769399","tid":151960,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T14:16:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a37bcd47f4f4a7d21497c054f5558c0024829b1e","tid":151960,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T06:06:55.000Z","msg":"巴打有冇SEED? 搵左好耐好想看<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9eb042b8e57a591437287446fe30fcfc9161a4c","tid":151960,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T06:06:55.000Z","msg":"巴打有冇SEED? 搵左好耐好想看<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}